name: OCKLabeledValue
desc: A label that is paired with a value, which you use to represent information.

items.name: init(label: String, value: String)
items.desc: Creates a labeled value with an optional label and value.

items.name: var label: String
items.desc: A description of what the label is, for example, “Home Email”, “Office Phone”.

items.name: var value: String
items.desc: The actual contact information, for example, a phone number or email address.
